ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2014-15
PrecisAppointment of GASTON BARBAN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Madagascar, with residence in Pretoria; GINETTE MARTIN as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of the Congo, with residence in Kinshasa; and PHILIP PINNINGTON as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Serbia, with concurrent accreditation to Montenegro and to the Republic of Macedonia, with residence in Belgrade.
